  <div id="text-content_A79B0DD0-2217-0135-4B52-22000B5A851D" class="text-block-content">
    <p>As a student, you can create your own Student Groups for study groups, discuss an assignment, etc. You can be part of more than one student group. </p>
<p><strong>Note</strong>: If you cannot see the People tab in your course, or if you cannot see the Add Group button, your instructor has restricted this feature.</p>
  </div>
</div>

